#

Savory Herb-Infused Chicken Gravy Over Mashed Potatoes

$15.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteincomfort-food

Tags:

heartysatisfyinghomemade

Description

Tender chicken smothered in a rich, herby gravy served over creamy mashed potatoes for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken thighs: 2 lbs
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
  • unsalted butter: 4 tbsp
  • all-purpose flour: 1/4 cup
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • potatoes (russet or Yukon gold): 2 lbs
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • dried thyme: 1 tsp
  • dried rosemary: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • chopped parsley: for garnish
